To install puppet

put the following in /etc/yum.repos.d/puppet.repo
[puppetlabs]
name=Puppet Labs Packages
baseurl=http://yum.puppetlabs.com/fedora/f15/products/x86_64/
enabled=0
gpgcheck=0

then run
sudo yum -y --enablerepo=puppetlabs install puppet

Instructions for adding a puppet rvm module
https://github.com/blt04/puppet-rvm

